WEBVTT

00:00.349 --> 00:05.254
I am a witch's cat and Shadow is my name.

00:06.133 --> 00:10.556
Don't ever try to stroke me for I was never tame.

00:11.648 --> 00:13.814
My fur is black as jet.

00:14.578 --> 00:16.777
My eyes are piercing white.

00:17.770 --> 00:21.825
If I cross your path, I may give you a fright.

00:23.194 --> 00:27.441
I am a working cat; there is no time to play.

00:28.249 --> 00:33.083
I must make sure all spells are cast in the right way.

00:34.160 --> 00:38.593
The witch relies upon me much more I need not say.

00:39.381 --> 00:44.227
So if you spot me passing just quickly walk away.

